reviewText: Another great DVD produced by Lee and Tiffany...You buy hunting DVD's to see the monsters killed and this is exactly what you get with WTF6...Their hard work and dedication preparing for the season pays off with the big bucks that they take... Thanks for such a great DVD Lee and Tiffany and i cant wait to buy WTF 7...
Same great footage as we came to expect in Whitetail Freaks 1 through 5. These folks can always be depended on to produce the highest quality deer hunting videos. You won't be disappointed.
